Package: mc-rcon
Version: 0.2.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Dylan Bulmer <dylan@bulmer.dev>
Depends: mc-server
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://apt.bulmer.dev
Description: RCON subcommand plugin for mc-server
 mc-rcon adds the 'mc rcon' subcommand to the mc CLI, providing interactive
 RCON console access and single-command execution against a running Minecraft
 server. Implemented in C with no runtime dependencies beyond mc-server.
